lead_paragraph: An Italian gossip magazine on Monday became the latest outlet to publish images of the Duchess of Cambridge, the former Kate Middleton, sunbathing topless in France.

headline.seo: Italian Magazine Publishes Topless Images of Kate Middleton
headline.main: Italian Magazine Publishes Disputed Images of Duchess
headline.print_headline: Italy: Magazine Publishes Images of British Duchess

abstract: Italian gossip magazine Chi becomes the latest outlet to publish images of the Duchess of Cambridge, the former Kate Middleton, sunbathing topless while on a vacation in France.
snippet: An Italian gossip magazine on Monday became the latest outlet to publish images of the Duchess of Cambridge, the former Kate Middleton, sunbathing topless in France.

byline.contributor: Elisabetta Povoledo reported from Rome, and Alan Cowell from London.
byline.original: By ELISABETTA POVOLEDO and ALAN COWELL
